                    <h1>Documents</h1>
                    <p>In the course of preparing <em>Toward “Thorough, Accurate, and
                            Reliable,”</em> Joshua Botts, author of the chapters covering recent
                        decades, relied on many documents that had not yet been released to the
                        public. All those documents have now been reviewed for declassification and
                        approved for release; in some cases, documents were released with excisions.
                        Over the coming year, the Office of the Historian will periodically post
